TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ;with samba_account as( select accountkey childid , isnull(measure_reference , accountdescriptionshort) child , parentaccountkey ,cast ('Slobs Cost' as varchar) parent from dbo.dimaccount with(nolock) where application_name = 'samba' and accountdescriptionshort = 'Slobs Cost' union all select chd.accountkey childid , isnull(chd.measure_reference , chd.accountdescriptionshort) child , chd.parentaccountkey , cast (isnull(par.measure_reference , par.accountdescriptionshort)as varchar) parent from (select * from dbo.dimaccount with(nolock) where application_name = 'samba' ) chd join (select * from dbo.dimaccount with(nolock) where application_name = 'samba' ) par on chd.parentaccountkey = par.accountkey join samba_account on chd.parentaccountkey = samba_account.childid ) select lower(child) measure_name from samba_account

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT [samba_meas].[measure_name] as MEASURE_NAME, LTRIM(RTRIM([xfer].[GL_Number])) as GL_Number FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT gl_number , measure_name_id FROM ( SELECT gl_number , measure_name_id
FROM [dbo].[Financial_Measure_GL_XRef]with(nolock)
UNION ALL
SELECT Reference_sub_key_1 , Reference_sub_key_2 FROM [dbo].[REFERENCE] with(nolock) WHERE Reference_key = 'GFSAdjAcctMap' ) a
)
xfer JOIN (SELECT ISNULL([measure_reference] , [accountdescriptionshort]) measure_name , ISNULL([measure_name_id],[accountkey]) accountkey FROM [dimaccount] with(nolock) WHERE [Application_Name] = 'SAMBA' ) samba_meas ON [xfer].[measure_name_id] = [samba_meas].[AccountKey]
